Subject: [PATCH 11/14] ARM: dts: imx6dl-colibri-eval-v3: disable PWM B/C/D

PWM is not really required by Toradex Easy Installer and might
interfere on some carrier boards. Disable it by default.

Signed-off-by: Gerard Salvatella <gerard.salvatella@toradex.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6dl-colibri-eval-v3.dts | 12 ------------
 1 file changed, 12 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6dl-colibri-eval-v3.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6dl-colibri-eval-v3.dts
index 0e27f180913b..49108e5c0f5a 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6dl-colibri-eval-v3.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx6dl-colibri-eval-v3.dts
@@ -199,22 +199,10 @@
 	remote-endpoint = <&lcd_display_in>;
 };
 
-&pwm1 {
-	status = "okay";
-};
-
-&pwm2 {
-	status = "okay";
-};
-
 &pwm3 {
 	status = "okay";
 };
 
-&pwm4 {
-	status = "okay";
-};
-
 &reg_usb_host_vbus {
 	status = "okay";
 };
